metadata.name: MTXME 1/1
metadata.description:
We are embarking on a new way of conducting business, particularly with our contracts. The goal is transparency between organizations.

In this way, we are minting a contract between an organization we are partnering with as an NFT. With the full details in the agreement being visible on our mirror entry.

In exchange for $5,000 USD in ETH on February 2022 and a token exchange to be discussed at later date, we (multi/title), will provide branding & identity services for MUST EXIT.
